    {
      "text": "Andre Agassi Tennis is a tennis video game released in 1993, starring tennis legend Andre Agassi. The game was released for the Super Nintendo Entertainment System, Genesis, Master System, and Game Gear. It enjoyed a much belated release for mobile phones.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Andre Agassi Tennis est un jeu vidéo de tennis sorti en 1992 et fonctionne sur Game Gear, Master System, Mega Drive et Super Nintendo. Le jeu a été développé par TecMagik puis édité par TecMagik et Lance Investments.\nLe jeu tient son nom du champion Andre Agassi.",
      "lang": "fr",
      "source": "wikipedia_fr"
    },
    {
      "text": "Andre Agassi Tennis è un videogioco di tennis distribuito nel 1992.\nIl gioco è stato sviluppato per Super Nintendo Entertainment System, Sega Mega Drive, Sega Master System e Game Gear per poi essere convertito per cellulari.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    }
